room_title: Escape room "Rendezvous at Dr. Frankenstein's" by Conundrum Escape Rooms in Durango
room_description: You have been invited to The Frankenstein Castle for a dinner party. Rumors have been floating around town about the strange events occurring there and out of curiosity, you have accepted the invitation. Now you and the other guests find yourselves trapped in the good Dr's office and a notice that Dr. Frankenstein is running late. You must rely on the brilliance of your team to comprehend the Dr.'s mad mind and escape before he returns.
